# sha1prng

SHA1PRNG在Python中的实现，与JAVA SecureRandom的生成结果保持一致。

## 安装

```shell
pip install sha1prng
```

## 使用

### Python测试代码

```python

import binascii
from sha1prng import SHA1PRNG

gen = SHA1PRNG(b"pwd")
for i in range(50):
    value = gen.randbytes(7)
    print(binascii.hexlify(value).decode())

```

